CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1945, pg. 5 reads: "Good Deed - Members of the Shadyside Community Club entertained Deshon Hospital veterans last Thursday evening in home of Mrs. Isadore Reid. Upper photo: The Deshon veterans are all set to cut a rug with lovely maids who came after the dinner to help make the boys feel at home... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group of men and women, including members of the Shadyside Community Club, entertaining Deshon Hospital veterans, gathered in home of Isadore Reid
